Saracens face Clermont Auvergne in the European Cup semi-final at Stade Geoffroy-Guichard on Saturday . 
  Mark McCall has named Brad Barritt as captain for the clash . 
  The two sides met in last year's semi-finals at Twickenham . 
  Saracens lost 46-6 in the quarter-final . 
  Owen Farrell has been named on the bench for the game . 
 